No. 975,

Mise.

DeMaro v. United States. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Marshall, Assistant Attorney General Vinson and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

C. A. 7th Cir. Certiorari denied.

The Chief Justice, Mr. Justice Brennan and Mr. Justice Fortas are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
